53A5B"></path></svg></span></span><img class="gallerySummary_itemImage" src="./bottle12_files/2b91d748f523c0a4d03ba7abd8b171da.jpg" alt="Review video by KAREN A." decoding="async" loading="lazy"></button></div></div></div><div class="reviewsSingle_body"><div class="css-y61c3o es2c2ru0"><ul class="reviewsList"><li class="reviewsList_item"><div class="css-1r7h4b3 e1vtkzrv0" data-review-id="124362837"><div class="reviewsItem_head"><h3 class="reviewsItem_title">Works perfect</h3><div class="reviewsItem_info"><div class="reviewsItem_infoItem isRating"><div class="css-cjg184 e1gsfhkj0" aria-label="Rated 5.0 out of 5 stars"><div class="reviewsRating"><span style="width: 100%;"></span></div></div></div><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isAuthor">Anonymous</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isVerified">Verified Buyer</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isMeta">Spain, <time datetime="01/03/2024">01/03/2024</time></span></div></div><div class="reviewsItem_body"><div>Had some trouble initally with my order but the customer service was excellent. Thank you very much.

The bottle works great and is a great addition to my travel lifestyle, especially filling up water at airport stations</div></div></div></li><li class="reviewsList_item"><div class="css-1r7h4b3 e1vtkzrv0" data-review-id="124357803"><div class="reviewsItem_head"><h3 class="reviewsItem_title">Outstanding</h3><div class="reviewsItem_info"><div class="reviewsItem_infoItem isRating"><div class="css-cjg184 e1gsfhkj0" aria-label="Rated 5.0 out of 5 stars"><div class="reviewsRating"><span style="width: 100%;"></span></div></div></div><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isAuthor">Brigitte B.</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isVerified">Verified Buyer</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isMeta">United States, <time datetime="01/03/2024">01/03/2024</time></span></div></div><div class="reviewsItem_body"><div>I love my bottle and was the perfect purchase for my trip to South America to give me peace of mind when refilling the bottle.</div></div></div></li><li class="reviewsList_item"><div class="css-1r7h4b3 e1vtkzrv0" data-review-id="124294081"><div class="reviewsItem_head"><h3 class="reviewsItem_title">Best travel bottle </h3><div class="reviewsItem_info"><div class="reviewsItem_infoItem isRating"><div class="css-cjg184 e1gsfhkj0" aria-label="Rated 5.0 out of 5 stars"><div class="reviewsRating"><span style="width: 100%;"></span></div></div></div><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isAuthor">MARTHA L.</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isVerified">Verified Buyer</span><span class="reviewsItem_infoItem isMeta">United States, <time datetime="01/02/2024">01/02/2024</time></span></div></div><div class="reviewsItem_body"><div>Best bottle on the market. Only change I would make is to make it lighter. Never travel without it</div></div></div></li></ul></div><div class="reviewsSingle_footer"><a href="https://www.livelarq.com/purification/larq-bottle-purevis/reviews" class="css-172pytf encln6v0">Read all 6309 reviews</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="css-38s40v e4b8vos0"><div class="css-5cev5b"><div class="css-gp474v"><div class="css-zhyymx e5ogd4o0"><div class="faqFeatured_head"><div class="css-1yz34h eb9aazh0"><h2 class="headingTitle">Just the FAQs</h2></div></div><div class="faqFeatured_body"><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">What's in the box?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content"> <ul class="inBox"> <li> <img src="./bottle12_files/LARQ_Website_FAQs_MDW.jpg" alt=""> <span>LARQ Bottle PureVis™</span> </li> <li> <img src="./bottle12_files/LARQ_Website_FAQs_USB.jpg" alt=""> <span>USB to MicroUSB connector</span> </li> <li> <img src="./bottle12_files/LARQ_Website_FAQs_QSG.jpg" alt=""> <span>Quick Start Guide</span> </li> </ul> </div></div></div></div><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">How to use LARQ Bottle PureVis™?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content"> <p>LARQ Bottle PureVis™ is easy to use.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Fill up anywhere</strong><br>The LARQ Bottle PureVis™ gives you the power to take brilliantly clean water with you everywhere you go.</li> <li><strong>Press the cap for PureVis™</strong><br>While you wait, give the bottle a gentle shake or do your best water dance to spread the PureVis™ light evenly.</li> <li><strong>And voila!</strong><br>Enjoy brilliantly clean water from a clean bottle. It's that simple.</li> </ul> </div></div></div></div><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">How does the LARQ Bottle PureVis™ work?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content">The LARQ Bottle PureVis uses PureVis™ technology to clean your water and bottle at the touch of a button. The bottle intelligently turns on every 2 hours to clean the water you put inside as well as the inside of the bottle.</div></div></div></div><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">Will the insulated LARQ Bottle PureVis™ keep the water cold?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content">Yes, the insulated bottle will keep cold water chilled for up to 24 hours.</div></div></div></div><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">Does the LARQ Bottle PureVis have a warranty?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content">LARQ offers a 1-year limited warranty on all bottles purchased from www.livelarq.com and authorized retailers. The warranty covers the repair or replacement of any defective material or component. In the rare case that we are unable to repair or replace the defective material or component, we will submit a refund. It does not cover any issues due to normal wear and tear, misuse or loss/theft of the bottle.</div></div></div></div><div class="css-c9vw98 e6c5f7n0"><button type="button" class="faqExpanderHead" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faqExpanderHead_inner"><span class="faqExpanderHead_indicator"><span class="indicatorEl horizontal"></span><span class="indicatorEl vertical"></span></span><div class="faqExpanderHead_title">Where can I find the manual?</div></div></button><div class="faqExpanderBody" style="opacity: 0; height: 0px; visibility: hidden;"><div class="faqExpanderBody_inner"><div class="faqExpanderBody_content">You will find manual in your box or you can <a target="_blank" href="https://res.cloudinary.com/larq/image/upload/v1652372108/manual/New%20version/LARQ_Bottle_PureVis_Online-Manual_Ver-7_220512.pdf">download it here!</a></div></div></div></div><div class="faqFeatured_footer"><a aria-label="Opens support page" href="https://www.livelarq.com/support" class="css-172pytf encln6v0">See all FAQs</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="css-pq5qpk e4b8vos0"><div class="css-161o70f"><div class="css-gp474v"><div class="css-4cffwv"><div class="css-1g231j7"><div class="css-1d0ax0j eb9aazh0"><h2 class="headingTitle">Technology</h2></div></div></div><div class="css-181zoys"><div class="css-a4lnj2"><div class="css-1rbqkfv exvjhuk0"><div class="cardHead"><img src="./bottle12_files/technology_1.png" alt="PureVis technology battery" decoding="async" loading="lazy"></div><div class="cardBody"><div class="cardBody_title"><div class="css-16gxt67 eb9aazh0"><h3 class="headingTitle"><span>PureVis™ technology</span></h3></div></div><div class="cardBody_text">Our proprietary PureVis™ technology makes on-the-go water purification possible.</div></div></div></div><div class="css-a4lnj2"><div class="css-1jub1dj exvjhuk0"><div class="cardHead"><button type="button" title="View Drink brilliantly video" class="cardHead_imageVideoBtn"><img src="./bottle12_files/tecnology_2.png" alt="Video showing larq bottle vs traditional bottle" decoding="async" loading="lazy"><span class="cardHead_videoIcon"><span color="text.default" class="css-11qxqh7 e1evajc90"><svg class="css-82n8sf eks92ln0" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 80 80" color="text.default" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="80" height="80" rx="40" fill="white"></rect><path d="M51.375 38.0781L34.875 28.3281C33.5156 27.5312 31.5 28.3281 31.5 30.25V49.75C31.5 51.5312 33.375 52.6094 34.875 51.7188L51.375 41.9688C52.8281 41.0781 52.8281 38.9688 51.375 38.0781Z" fill="#153A5B"></path></svg></span></span></button></div><div class="cardBody"><div class="cardBody_title"><div class="css-16gxt67 eb9aazh0"><h3 class="headingTitle"><span>Drink brilliantly</span></h3></div></div><div class="cardBody_text">PureVis™ is lab-tested to neutralize up to 99% of bacteria such as E.coli. <a href="https://res.cloudinary.com/larq/image/upload/v1641848705/assets/spa/pdf/LARQ_Efficacy_Data_E.coli.pdf" title="Learn more" target="_blank">Learn more</a>.</div></div></div></div><div class="css-a4lnj2"><div class="css-1rbqkfv exvjhuk0"><div class="cardHead"><img src="./bottle12_files/technology_3.png" alt="Showing how UV-C light works inside the Larq purevis™ bottle" decoding="async" loading="lazy"></div><div class="cardBody"><div class="cardBody_title"><div class="css-16gxt67 eb9aazh0"><h3 class="headingTitle"><span>How it works</span></h3></div></div><div class="cardBody_text">UV-C light damages the nucleic acids in the DNA, deactivating germs.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="css-9pr3m6"><div class="css-a4lnj2"><div class="css-1n1rfw0 e1yu41lc0"><div class="cardHead"><span color="text.default" size="70" class="css-1r4ci78 e1evajc90"><svg class="css-82n8sf eks92ln0" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 48 48" color="text.default" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="#F3756D" d="M24 5.8C34 5.8 42.2 14 42.2 24S34 42.2 24 42.2 5.8 34 5.8 24 14 5.8 24 5.8M24 4C13 4 4 13 4 24s9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20S35 4 24 4z"></path><path fill="#F3756D" stroke="#F3756D" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M10.6 10.6l26.8 26.8"></path><path fill="none" stroke="#F3756D" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M19.4 11.7h1.7v7.8L13.7 31s-1.1 1.8-.1 3.7c.8 1.5 2.5 1.5 2.5 1.5H24M28.6 11.7h-1.7v7.8L34.3 31s1.1 1.8.1 3.7c-.8 1.5-2.5 1.5-2.5 1.5H24"></path><path fill="#F3756D" d="M30.5 34.1h-13c-1.3 0-2.2-1.5-1.4-2.6l4.2-6.7h7.4l4.3 6.8c.6 1-.2 2.5-1.5 2.5"></path><path fill="none" stroke="#F3756D" stroke-width=".816" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M21.2 13.6h2M21.1 15.3h1.5M21.4 17h2M21.1 18.8h1.5"></path><path fill="#F3756D" d="M27.9 12h-1.1c-.1 0-.2-.1-.2-.2s.1-.2.2-.2h1.1c.1 0 .2.1.2.2.1.1 0 .2-.2.2zM21.2 12h-1.1c-.1 0-.2-.1-.2-.2s.1-.2.2-.2h1.1c.1 0 .2.1.2.2s-.1.2-.2.2z"></path></svg></span></div><div class="cardBody"><div class="cardBody_title"><div class="css-16gxt67 eb9aazh0"><h3 class="headingTitle"><span>Chemical free</span></h3></div></div><div class="cardBody_text">Non-toxic purification with zero additives</div></div></div></div><div class="css-a4lnj2"><div class="css-1n1rfw0 e1yu41lc0"><div class="cardHead"><span color="text.default" size="70" class="css-1r4ci78 e1evajc90"><svg class="css-82n8sf eks92ln0" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 48 48" color="text.default" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="#F3756D" d="M24 5.8C34 5.8 42.2 14 42.2 24S34 42.2 24 42.2 5.8 34 5.8 24 14 5.8 24 5.8M24 4C13 4 4 13 4 24s9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20S35 4 24 4z"></path><path fill="#F3756D" stroke="#F3756D" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M10.6 10.6l