s92ln0" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 42 26" color="text.default" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M28.707.293l12 12L40 13l.707.707-12 12-1.414-1.414L37.586 14H0v-2h37.586L27.293 1.707 28.707.293z" fill="#153A5B"></path></svg></span></button><div class="css-13gnxt8 eem0ch90"><div class="content"><div class="contentInner"><div class="content_head"><h3 class="content_headTitle">LARQ Bottle PureVis™ Insulated</h3></div><div class="content_body"><div class="content_bodyContent"><p>The LARQ Bottle PureVis™ Insulated is the world's first self-cleaning water bottle and water purification system. It uses PureVis™ technology to eliminate up to 99%* of bio-contaminants such as E. coli from your water and bottle. Double-wall vacuum insulation keeps your water cold for 24 hours and hot for 12.</p></div><div class="content_bodyNotes css-1u3emem e1bohh7j0"><div class="notes_item"><div class="notes_itemAstrix"></div><div class="notes_itemText">Based on elimination 99.8% of E.coli in a 20-second cycle for all LARQ Bottles.</div></div></div><div class="content_bodyFeatures css-13fu61e e1tr28oi0"><div class="featuresSection_listItem"><div class="featuresSection_listItem_icon"><span color="text.default" class="css-11qxqh7 e1evajc90"><svg class="css-82n8sf eks92ln0" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 44 50" color="text.default" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22.914 13.176a1.514 1.514 0 00-.94-.366 1.41 1.41 0 00-.94.418 1.514 1.514 0 00-.365.94v9.188a4.594 4.594 0 102.662 0v-9.189a1.41 1.41 0 00-.417-.991zm.991 14.513a1.878 1.878 0 01-1.931 1.931 1.931 1.931 0 01-1.932-1.931 1.984 1.984 0 011.932-1.932 1.931 1.931 0 011.931 1.931z" fill="#EE706A"></path><path d="M40.716 27.689a1.355 1.355 0 001.252 1.618 1.303 1.303 0 001.306-1.357 21.143 21.143 0 00-5.22-14.148l1.252-1.253 1.41 1.462.313.313c.262.226.594.355.94.366a1.41 1.41 0 00.94-.366 1.306 1.306 0 000-1.88l-2.298-2.348-3.132-3.133a1.41 1.41 0 00-.888-.417 1.357 1.357 0 00-.94 2.297l1.828 1.827-1.253 1